  ('attended', 6, 'Akash', 'E commerce', 'Client operates a cosmetics and perfume distribution business that has been running for approximately 3.5 years and works with around 35 vendors. The company imports products from suppliers and distributes them through an established offline B2B network while using Tally for accounting, inventory, sales, and purchase management. The founder currently manages all customer communication manually, including product enquiries, stock availability, pricing, discounts, offers, and order confirmations, resulting in significant time consumption and limiting business scalability. The client is also facing issues with overbooking fast-moving SKUs because orders are confirmed without validating real-time inventory, while inventory planning is done manually by analysing previous sales data in Tally, leading to only partially accurate demand forecasting. The immediate requirement is to develop an AI-powered WhatsApp Sales Assistant capable of answering customer queries, searching products and SKUs, sharing product catalogues with images, providing pricing, discounts, stock availability, product recommendations, FAQs, order enquiries, and supporting seamless human handoff for complex or bulk order conversations through a configurable hybrid AI-human workflow. Additionally, the client requires an Inventory Analytics and Forecasting Dashboard integrated with Tally to analyse daily, weekly, and monthly sales trends, identify fast-moving and slow-moving products, forecast future demand, recommend reorder quantities, monitor inventory health, generate stock alerts, assist in purchase planning, and provide business intelligence dashboards for better decision-making. In future phases, the client plans to implement a fully customized CRM/ERP system including Customer Management, Vendor Management, Product Management, Purchase Orders, Sales Orders, Inventory Management, Invoice Generation, Payment Tracking, WhatsApp and Email Notifications, Workflow Automation, Reporting, Analytics, User Roles, and AI-driven business insights. The overall objective is to reduce founder dependency, automate repetitive customer interactions, prevent inventory overbooking, improve operational efficiency, enhance customer response time, and build a scalable digital infrastructure that supports long-term business growth.', NULL, 'initial stage', 'proposal sent ; client is not ok with the budget', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '832 956 6438'),
